Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱約感覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  古籍研究社的文化祭不可能一帆風順結束  這才是傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別留下這種麻煩的傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是那樣  至少給個護身符吧  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說「謝謝」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便告訴你  筆裡沒墨水了  而且筆尖摔折了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拿廢物呼嚨人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有空我會去看看情況的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  你別來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭要來啦  奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是老樣子  奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是興致勃勃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這可是社團的傳統  神山高中文化祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個背影不是摩耶花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計那是漫畫研究社的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花她們也打扮得充滿節日氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是也有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是手藝社的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  摩耶花  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別誇我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼的Cospl……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在普通同學的面前不要用那個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  這是什麼裝束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙洛露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙洛露？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙洛露貝利切莉芙洛露？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20}註：出自  萩尾望都老師的科幻漫畫《第11人》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  稍後還要帶手套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的包裡都裝了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花一整天都待在漫畫研究社嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因為接受了攤位販賣的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去多想那件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情已經發生  那也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是文化祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然聽說過  但這遠超出我的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼  做工好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱鬧過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  要大幹一場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先在這裡告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去手藝社嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微去露個臉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我馬上會趕過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好安靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太糾結了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你一直糾結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志姑且不說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田也會開始糾結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.59,BOOK12,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs20\pos(230,119)}古籍研究社  社刊\N\N\N\N\N\N「冰菓」\h第四十六號刊\N\N  發售中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  折木同學  摩耶花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是靠努力就能解決的狀況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不能保證努力就能解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可以保證  如果不努力什麼都不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您所言極是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是由我買下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的並不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是印刷是我下的訂單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本預定印刷多少冊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十冊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際送到的數量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩百冊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀河～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(310,325)}Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我的土星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(355,325)}Saturn
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  還沒開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我沒有確認印刷廠發來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都會犯錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這副打扮還去安慰別人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用一個人難過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都是夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這副打扮還去安慰別人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作為社長  也應該進行再次確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是交了原稿就不聞不問了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是古籍研究社全體的責任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我就是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你終於明白了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了  你這副打扮還去安慰別人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  馬上就到開幕式了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼才能將銷售量提到最高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家有沒有什麼好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每冊單價是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二百日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經很便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題在於古籍研究社缺乏知名度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地理位置也太偏僻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:10:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  大前提是提高知名度以及在更好的地方設攤位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在其他的地方設攤位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光是一心一意想著如何能把客人引導到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學運用了逆向思維啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這算不上逆向思維吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但文化祭都已經開始了  這種事情能獲得批准嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼想  總務委員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種特權不知能不能獲得認可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接去找我們委員長或學生會長申請試試如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總務委員長是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你至少讀讀指南手冊吧  奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}委員長  田名邊治朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  我還希望你可以注意到這個順序呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  是不是很引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  古籍研究社排在所有社團介紹的最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我硬求給安排在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為指南手冊是總務委員會編排的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是濫用職權吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想見委員長的話  去會議室看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能由你去拜託嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這也是一種辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我對交涉沒有太大信心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由千反田來提出申請  我在一旁幫著說些好話如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請幫幫我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不是很積極啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個  我更想去做宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才穿成這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是其一  我還有其他的秘策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在文化祭中開展的各項比賽裡  以古籍研究社的名義參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能取得優異成績的話  古籍研究社的知名度也會上升
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想自己玩得開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}真不愧是福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這確實是個好主意  現在確定方針了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田去進行申請新攤位的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志負責宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先這麼行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  折木同學你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責看店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…的確得留個人在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  差不多走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開幕式的點名就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  就按剛才的任務分配開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爭取多賣一本是一本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是「冰菓」二百本全部賣完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  嘿  喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎題研究社進展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我宣布第五十四屆KANYA祭開幕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  跳過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  轉起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是興奮的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要練練書法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書法耶  書法喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要練練書法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}好地產好米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的話  留作紀念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去不行  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筑波嶺峰上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春盡夏已至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟程道揚鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}神出鬼沒！！  歡迎初學者  百人一首社
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久違…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去不行  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}總務委員會本部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…請問有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  我來找總務委員長的田名邊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是田名邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  那麼…請為古籍研究社增加銷售攤位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國際活動社
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國際活動社
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我是古籍研究社社長千反田愛瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請為古籍研究社增加銷售攤位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼突然地來申請  我也沒辦法立即同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  等等  那只是從原則上講而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼緣由的話  可以說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得福部同學好像說交涉時會來幫忙來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我說  能踩油門就走唄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  不成  不成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是危險人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因就是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這的確很辛苦啊  我也想幫幫你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  每個社團都有難處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能只對古籍研究社特殊照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果請其它社團在他們攤位幫忙代售古籍研究社社刊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不會干涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個好方法啊  我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  伊原  你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河內學姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連短刀都配備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是塑膠做的仿製品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是鞋子也下番功夫就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼嘛  到頭來不也還是Cosplay嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明之前那麼反對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一開始就按河內說的做該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊  湯淺學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  社長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花錢了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是買了腰帶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有發票的話記得給我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  社長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不好開口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託在這裡代售《冰菓》什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這扮的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  是芙洛露喔  你知道《第11人》嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  我都沒聽說過耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是挺久以前的SF漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得是部名作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  要借什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫畫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  大家加油幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  已經開店了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一號客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看店萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先把肯定能賣出去的寫上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據現狀考慮  古籍研究社四人每人買兩本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後加上顧問老師以及保存用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共計12本是一定能賣出的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實  只賣掉這些也不算少了
