Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}咦  有誰看見我的蘋果汁了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}沒看見耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}唉  我還一口沒喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}那張紙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}不  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}比起這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
