Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  龐克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.36,0:22:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是龐克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是幹嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不  在賣社刊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這全都是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那賣我一本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  客人？是客人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得熱情一點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  根本沒笑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  能讓我看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是服裝研究會的  正準備做流行時裝表演
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.16,0:23:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是正裝系的胸袋配飾讓我給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正已經是廢物了  請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們表演的優先券
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著這個來服裝研究會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會為你配搭最棒的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去也只有里志會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.85,0:23:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那傢伙也有他的執著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之是賣出一本了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
